nodes.text: The Edjian Prince was a mythical Corellian figure who braved the unknown forests of the Uhl Eharl Khoehng. The Edjian Prince was one such legend on Corellia that predated the Old Republic and helped define the spirit of adventure and exploration that became essential parts of Corellian heritage. The Coronet Spaceport had a relief sculpture depicting the Edijan Prince.
